{
  "texts": [
    "These files cover the six official languages, namely Arabic, Chinese, English, French, Russian, and Spanish.",
    "Some of the files also provide versions in German.",
    "• ParaCrawl (Bañón et al, 2020).",
    "ParaCrawl utilizes open-source software to crawl webpages, creating a publicly available parallel corpus.",
    "The corpus of version 5.0 includes 223M filtered sentence pairs from approximately 150K websites, encompassing 42 languages."
  ]
}